modName: West Wind Combat Series - Misfit Mage - Conversion  UNPB UNP BBP BBPx TBBP
summary: A conversion of Misfit Mage by brokefoot to UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx/UNPB-TBBP/UNP-BBP with working weight slider
descriptionHtml:
This is a conversion of Misfit Mage by brokefoot to UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx/UNPB-TBBP/UNP-BBP It requires Brokefoot's original mod. This is only Mesh and weight changes for the UNPB/UNP-BBP body type. Working weight slider.

Install Brokefoot's mod first [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36780]West Wind Combat Series - Misfit Mage UNP[/url] then overwrite the files for the body type you want.
